{"parse":{"title":"greetings","pageid":200143,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"==English==\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|en|/ˈɡɹiːtɪŋz/}}\n* {{hyph|en|greet|ings}}\n* {{audio|en|En-us-greetings.oga|a=US}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{head|en|noun form}}\n\n# {{plural of|en|greeting}}\n\n===Interjection===\n{{en-intj}}\n\n# {{lb|en|sometimes|formal|sometimes|humorous}} [[hello|Hello]].\n#* {{quote-av|en|writer=[[w:Daniel Waters (screenwriter)|Daniel Waters]]|director=w:Michael Lehmann|actor=w:Christian Slater|role=Jason Dean|title=w:Heathers|year=1989|time=11:50|text='''Greetings''' and salutations. You a Heather?}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|formal way of saying \"hello\"}}\n* Dutch: {{t+|nl|saluut}}, {{t+|nl|gegroet}}\n* French: {{t+|fr|salutations}}\n* German: {{t+|de|Grüße}}\n* Gothic: {{t|got|𐌷𐌰𐌹𐌻𐍃}}\n* Greek: {{t+|el|χαίρετε}}\n* Italian: {{t+|it|saluti}}\n* Kapampangan: {{t|pam|luid}}\n* Old East Slavic: {{t|orv|поклонъ}}\n* Portuguese: {{t+|pt|saudações}}\n* Spanish: {{t+|es|saludos}}, {{t+|es|saludes}}\n* Swedish: {{t+|sv|var hälsad}}\n* Tamil: {{t+|ta|வணக்கம்}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n===Anagrams===\n* {{anagrams|en|a=eegginrst|geestring|gingerest|regesting}}\n\n{{cln|en|greetings}}"}}